Haver version 0.06 ('Lamp')
==================

This is a collection of modules
used by both haver servers and haver clients.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   perl Build
   perl Build test
   perl Build install



DEPENDENCIES

YAML

